      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 275,
      "message": "You already had a working method. What changed is that you're now calling its body in a loop. Why didn't you change the client code? I mean it probably would be easier to write: \n\nfor (ComponentMonitoringUploadInfo uploadInfo : componentMonitoringUploadInfoList) {\n    enrichComponentMib(uploadInfo, vspId, version, errors);\n}\n\nWould be easier to compare/merge, too.",
